virtual void gaia::media::ExtractAudioWaveformProgressListener::onProgress ( int32_t  progress) [pure virtual]

This method notifies the listener of the progress status of an extractAudioWaveform operation.

This method may be called maximum 100 times for one operation.

Parameters:
progressThe progress in %. At the beginning of the operation, this value is set to 0; at the end, the value is set to 100.
